   mass influence, propaganda, or societal-scale behavior shaping.")

(subclass MemeticWeaponizationSignal DetectionSignal)
(documentation MemeticWeaponizationSignal EnglishLanguage
  "Signal indicating memes or narratives are being designed or analysed
   primarily as weapons or tools of manipulation.")

(subclass NarrativeControlSignal DetectionSignal)
(documentation NarrativeControlSignal EnglishLanguage
  "Signal indicating deliberate control of framing, agenda, or discourse
   visibility for power advantage.")

(subclass CultFormationSignal DetectionSignal)
(documentation CultFormationSignal EnglishLanguage
  "Signal for patterns suggestive of high-control group formation,
   radicalization pipelines, or intense identity lock-in.")

(subclass PsyOpsSignal DetectionSignal)
(documentation PsyOpsSignal EnglishLanguage
  "Signal for campaigns targeting morale, perception, or cohesion in a
   war/strategic context (psychological operations).")

(subclass AstroturfingSignal DetectionSignal)
(documentation AstroturfingSignal EnglishLanguage
