   coordination posing as spontaneous public sentiment.")

(subclass RecommenderHijackSignal DetectionSignal)
(documentation RecommenderHijackSignal EnglishLanguage
  "Signal indicating attempts to exploit or reconfigure recommender
   systems to amplify specific content or narratives.")

